I found the issue. I was missing the export of the methods. 

I added: 

    export const {Provider, Context} = CreateDataContext (
        authReducer,
        {signIn, signOut, signup},
        {isSignedIn: false, errorMessage: &#39;&#39;}
    );

and the method is now visible!

